 </sub>) due to a disease 
 <italic class="italic">j</italic> for each 0.5° grid 
 <italic class="italic">i</italic> attributable to ambient PM
 <sub class="sub">2.5</sub> exposure has been estimated for each decade starting from 2011 to 2100 using the traditional epidemiological relation
 <sup class="sup">
  <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR10" class="xref">10</xref>
 </sup>. as in Eq. 4
 <disp-formula id="Equ4" class="disp-formula">
